'''比爾人'''（Bhils)，是[[印度|印度]]中部主要的部落民族，人口主要集中在[[拉賈斯坦邦|拉賈斯坦邦]]、[[古吉拉特邦|古吉拉特邦]]、[[馬哈拉施特拉邦|馬哈拉施特拉邦]]、[[中央邦|中央邦]]，少部分分布於印度的南部和東部，例如，[[安得拉邦|安得拉邦]]、[[卡納塔克邦|卡納塔克邦]]、[[特里普拉邦|特里普拉邦]]。總共約一千多萬人，是印度的第三大部落民族<ref>{{Cite web
|url= http://www.encyclopedia.com/doc/1G2-3458000461.html
|title= Encyclopedia of World Cultures
|accessdate= 2015-07-26
|archive-date= 2016-09-03
|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160903152151/http://www.encyclopedia.com/doc/1G2-3458000461.html
|dead-url= no
}}</ref>。比爾人被認為是印度最早的本地人，他們不但比[[雅利安人|雅利安人]]早，甚至可能比[[達羅毗荼人|達羅毗荼人]]還早。後來外人反客為主，比爾人被迫退到印度山區裡<ref>{{cite book|editor = 林之满 萧枫|title = 浑厚深沉的古印度文明|publisher = 青蘋果數據中心|year = 2014|url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=80ytAgAAQBAJ&pg=PT71&lpg=PT71&dq=%E6%AF%94%E7%88%BE%E4%BA%BA+%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6&source=bl&ots=1iOGW0P0Td&sig=t-bmu57R7vhUpobOe4EhWiGxIXg&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ei=mjVKVdyKIYaxmAX4hYH4BQ&ved=0CD8Q6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=%E6%AF%94%E7%88%BE%E4%BA%BA%20%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6&f=false|access-date = 2015-05-06|archive-date = 2016-04-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160403015827/https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=80ytAgAAQBAJ&pg=PT71&lpg=PT71&dq=%E6%AF%94%E7%88%BE%E4%BA%BA+%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6&source=bl&ots=1iOGW0P0Td&sig=t-bmu57R7vhUpobOe4EhWiGxIXg&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ei=mjVKVdyKIYaxmAX4hYH4BQ&ved=0CD8Q6AEwBg#v=onepage&q=%E6%AF%94%E7%88%BE%E4%BA%BA%20%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6&f=false|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

